quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Gom…óii malaama gom…óin…ďe …ďen
  23,2,∆Āen huloo…ďe ka nder Julde ma…ď…ďe ko…ďe yankinii…ďe
  23,3,E …ďen …óurnii…ďe gaayi rayrayti( bolle meere)
  23,4,E …ďen ittoo…ďe jakka on
  23,5,E …ďen reenu…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  23,6,"Si wanaa e dow sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum …ďe √Īaame ma…ď…ďe …óen jeyi(horbe), haray kam…ďe …ďe wonaa feletee…ďe"
  23,7,"On mo …óa…ď…ďi …ďaawo …óum, haray ko …ďen woni jaggitoo…ďe …ďen"
  23,8,E …ďen aynu…ďe koolaaje ma…ď…ďe e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin
  23,9,E …ďen …ďe ka√Īun ko…ďe reenu…ďe e dow Jul…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen
  23,10,"∆Āee [sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo] ko kam…ďe woni ronoo…ďe …ďen"
  23,11,∆Āen ronoyay…ďe Firdawsi on kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe e nder makko
  23,12,Gom…óii Men tagii ne…ó…óanke on immorde e lasili loopal
  23,13,"Refti Men wa…ói mo to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] e nder √Īii…ďirde hu…ďindiinde"
  23,14,"Refti Men Tagi to…ď…ďere nden he…ó…óere, Men Tagi he…ó…óere nden huyre, Men Tagi huyre nden ∆īi'e, Men holtini ∆īi'e …óen teewu. Refti Men fu…ó…óanii mo Tagu woo, barkanii Alla Mo∆ī∆īo Tagu…óo"
  23,15,Refti onon …ďaawo …óum ko on maayoo…ďe
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon √Ďalnde Darngal on imminoyte"
  23,17,"Gom…óii Men Tagii dow moo…óon …óati jee…ói…ói, Men wonaali kadi welsindii…ďe gaayi tagu ngun"
  23,18,"Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagu ngun], Men ndewni …óam ka leydi, pellet, Menen ko Men Hattan…ďe e dow na…ďugol …óam"
  23,19,"Men fu…ó…óani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on nder ton dim…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko e majje √Īaamoton"
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hingal fu…óina gu∆īam [nebban wujetee…óam] e li'am [maafir…óam] wonannde √Īaamoo…ďe"
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraa…ói …óin tasakuyee, Me…óen yarna on go…ó…óun e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafaaji …óuu…óu…ói, ko immorde e majji kadi √Īaamoton"
  23,22,Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laa…óe …óen ronndete…óon
  23,23,"Gom…óii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďen, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, rewee Alla. Rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. Enee, on hulatah"
  23,24,"Hooree…ďe mbatu ngun wi'ani …ďen yeddu…ďe immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"Oo wonaali si ko o …ďanndinke yeru mo'on himo faalaa nde o …ďurnotoo e dow moo…óon. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaa…ďe, men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ďe amen aran…ďe …ďen"
  23,25,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'un, habbitee mo tun haa see…óa"
  23,26,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko …ďe fennimi kon"
  23,27,"Men wahayini faade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka Amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore Amen nden arii hu…ď…ďinirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naadu e nder makka immorde e kala nooneeji …óin …ói…ói-…ói…ói. E koreeji ma, si wanaa …ďen konngol ngol aditii e mu'un, wata a haaldu e am fii …ďen too√Īu…ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe yooletee…ďe"
  23,28,"Si a fotondirii an e …ďen wonndu…ďe e maa…óa e dow laana kan, haray maaku: \"Yettoore nden ko Alla woodani, On danndu…óo Men immorde e yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  23,29,"Maaku: \"Joomam, jippinam e jipporde barkinaande ko An woni Mo∆ī∆īo Jippinoowo"
  23,30,"Pellet, no e nder …óum [ko jaŇčtaa …óoo] Aayeeje, haysi men laatike ko men jarribotoo…ďe"
  23,31,Refti Men fu…ó…ói …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe yiirde wo…ď…ďe goo
  23,32,"Men Nulii e ma…ď…ďe Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, …óum woni Rewee Alla, rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. E on hulatah [Mo]"
  23,33,"Batu e yim…ďe makko …ďen yeddu…ďe …ďe fenni hawroygol e Laakara on, Men neemini …ďe ka ngurdan aduna wi*i: \"Oo wonaali si wanaa …ďanndunke yeru moo…óon himo √Īaama ko √Īaamoton kon himo yara kadi ko yaroton kon"
  23,34,"Mi woondii si on …óoftike …ďanndinke yeru mo'on, pellet, haray onon ontuma ko on hayru…ďe(pertube)"
  23,35,"Enee, o fodu on wonndema onon si on maayii on laatike mbullaari e ∆īi'e, wonndema onon ko on yaltinoytee…ďe"